headline: 5 Consumer Staples Giants to Buy Amid the Sector's Strong Momentum
summary: Consumer staples are surging in 2026 as investors rotate to value, lifting XLP 13.2% YTD and spotlighting EL, HSY, KMB, MNST and NYT with renewed momentum.
